{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"257","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"家樂福攜手聯合利華 「續食聯盟」 盼減205噸剩食","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p style='margin: 20px 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Meiryo, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑体, 微軟雅黑體, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Arial, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, 黑体, 黑體; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify;'>惜食風潮再掀回響，<a href='https://udn.com/search/tagging/2/%E5%AE%B6%E6%A8%82%E7%A6%8F' rel='110914' style='color: rgb(0, 84, 166); text-decoration-line: none; outline: none;'><span style='color: rgb(136, 136, 136); text-decoration-line: underline;'>家樂福</span></a>今與國際知名食品業者「聯合利華」攜手組成「續食聯盟」，提倡食物零浪費觀念。聯合利華旗下食品品牌「康寶」18日起也推出活動，預計捐贈10萬份濃湯調理包給<a href='https://udn.com/search/tagging/2/%E9%A3%9F%E7%89%A9%E9%8A%80%E8%A1%8C' rel='105273' style='color: rgb(0, 84, 166); text-decoration-line: none; outline: none;'><span style='color: rgb(136, 136, 136); text-decoration-line: underline;'>食物銀行</span></a>，估計雙方企業一年將減少205噸食物浪費，有11萬戶次的<a href='https://udn.com/search/tagging/2/%E5%BC%B1%E5%8B%A2%E5%AE%B6%E5%BA%AD' rel='103659' style='color: rgb(0, 84, 166); text-decoration-line: none; outline: none;'><span style='color: rgb(136, 136, 136); text-decoration-line: underline;'>弱勢家庭</span></a>受惠。</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 20px 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Meiryo, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑体, 微軟雅黑體, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Arial, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, 黑体, 黑體; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify;'>家樂福是國內第一家響應惜食觀念的量販業者。2016年起，率先與台北市忠勤里合作，在南機場社區成立續食餐廳「書屋花甲」，不定期以格外品、醜食材，製作續食餐點；同時，社區志工會前往鄰近家樂福門市，蒐集每日的新鮮剩食，一周五日固定開火，供周邊弱勢家庭里民一餐溫飽。</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 20px 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Meiryo, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑体, 微軟雅黑體, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Arial, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, 黑体, 黑體; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify;'>餐廳門外也放置一台「食享冰箱」，讓十五家合作店家，包括吳寶春麵包店，將每日賣剩的熟食麵包、饅頭等，無償供需要的人領取。忠勤里里長方荷生估計，執行一年半時間，已省下30萬噸食物。</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 20px 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Meiryo, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑体, 微軟雅黑體, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Arial, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, 黑体, 黑體; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify;'>家樂福文教基金會執行長蘇小真說，自2年前續食行動展開以來，已捐出約335公噸食材供大眾再利用，但國內每年仍浪費400萬噸食物，「努力的空間還很大」；好消息是，今年起，「聯合利華」成為首位響應其計畫的廠商夥伴。</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 20px 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Meiryo, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑体, 微軟雅黑體, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Arial, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, 黑体, 黑體; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify;'>聯合利華旗下的「康寶」18日起將推出促銷活動，消費者只要購買其任兩件產品，企業就捐出一份濃湯調理包給食物銀行。蘇小真表示，由於許多加工食品，距離有效期限已不滿一至二個月，無法上架但仍可食用，此舉將減少浪費。</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 20px 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Meiryo, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑体, 微軟雅黑體, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Arial, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, 黑体, 黑體; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify;'>聯合利華永續發展暨企業傳播事務經理尤慈霞表示，康寶產品採全球潔淨標示（Clean Label）原則，要求配方簡單化、搭配最少加工製成，「以前翻到包裝背面，都是看不懂的化學名稱，但現在都看得懂了」；食材採購也以致力於永續栽種的農民為來源。</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 20px 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Meiryo, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑体, 微軟雅黑體, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Arial, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, 黑体, 黑體; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify;'>聯合利華董事總經理何盈德也表示，若每個人減少25％的剩食，就能餵飽全世界的人，惜食應從自身做起。</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 20px 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Meiryo, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑体, 微軟雅黑體, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Arial, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, 黑体, 黑體; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify;'><img alt='' src='/user_files/news_files/0423.jpg' style='width: 800px; height: 558px;' /><span style='color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Meiryo, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑体, 微軟雅黑體, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Arial, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, 黑体, 黑體; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify;'>家樂福總經理王俊超（左）與聯合利華董事總經理何盈德攜手組成「續食聯盟」。記者章凱閎／攝影</span></p>\n\n<p style='margin: 20px 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Meiryo, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑体, 微軟雅黑體, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Arial, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, 黑体, 黑體; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify;'>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 20px 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Meiryo, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑体, 微軟雅黑體, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Arial, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, 黑体, 黑體; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify;'><span style='color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Meiryo, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑体, 微軟雅黑體, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Arial, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, 黑体, 黑體; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify;'>資料來源:</span>https://udn.com/news/story/7266/3083128</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 20px 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Meiryo, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑体, 微軟雅黑體, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Arial, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, 黑体, 黑體; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify;'>&nbsp;</p>\n","keyword":"續食","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2018-04-23","clk_count":"310"}},"__N_SSG":true}